<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg Zenger zu Rosenberg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für das Schiedsgericht in wenigen Tagen mit Friedrich Zenger in Hersbruck, kündigt Teilnahme an und bittet um Georgs Anwesenheit. Im beigefügten Zettel wird die Zahlung des Botenlohns bestätigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_482" id="240v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_482_r1l1">Görgen <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_482_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg / Als Jr vns <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> habt </del> vnd den tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l3"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>kundt</expan> habt auf den <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Samſtag gen Herſprugk </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l4">als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen /. danken wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l5"><expan>fleiſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> müwe als Jr <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l6">habt / vnd vvöllen den tag alſo ſuchen / . vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l7">mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒe / daʒ Jr <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> dahin auf den tag auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l8"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / . vnd ob ıht darein viel daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l9">daʒ cʒe vviſſen tüt ſo Jr cʒeitlıchſt mügt / VVo wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l10"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb vnd dinſt beweiſen <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l11">vvir ſünderlıch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> vitȷ </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_482_r1l12">Cedula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_482_r1l13">Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> viiij groſʒ <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_482" id="240v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen <expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den tag
                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kundt</expan> habt <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                            <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> samstag</q>18.06.1412</note></app> gen Hersprugk, als
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen, danken wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> müwe, als ir <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
                        durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen habt, und wöllen den tag also
                        suchen. Und <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewch mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisze, daz ir
                            <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> dahin auf den tag auch
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, und ob iht darein viel, daz ir
                        uns daz cze wissen tüt, so ir czeitlichst mügt. Wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst beweisen
                                <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir sünderlich <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula<lb/> Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> viiii grosz <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
